			<h1>Rules</h1>
			<p class="maintxt">The rules of ICCMC and its Discord server are mostly just there because everyone else has them.</p>
			<h2>Minecraft rules</h2>
			<div style="padding-left: 5%; padding-right: 5%;">
				<ol>
					<li>Basic Minecraft Etiquette applies. (e.g: Don't steal from or attack a player or their property)</li>
					<li>Don't harm the server itself. (e.g: Don't spawn 3.2 million Chickens in the Spawn Chunks or use any hacks/exploits to lag/hurt the server)</li>
					<li>Don't make too big a mess with your builds (e.g: avoid spamming random blocks on the ground and leaving it), and try to light up your builds to avoid mob spawns where possible.</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
			<h2>Discord rules</h2>
			<div style="padding-left: 5%; padding-right: 5%;">
				<ol>
					<li>No NSFW. (Primarily images)</li>
					<li>Keep to the channel topic somewhat. Showcase your screenshots in <code>#screenshots</code>, talk about server issues in <code>#problems</code>, etc, at least.</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
			<br>
		</div>
